name: HACHI-KUN
description: The project is dedicated to honoring Kabosu's legacy by creating a vibrant community where fans can connect, share, and celebrate the Doge meme's enduring charm. HACHI, as Kabosu's loyal companion, symbolizes the deep bond and love that the community feels for Kabosu, helping to keep her story alive. Through various initiatives, including community events and content creation, the project aims to ensure that Kabosu's joyful spirit continues to inspire and bring happiness to people around the world.
